      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 Honda S2000 (AP2) in showroom condition. This example features the high-revving F22C1 2.2L DOHC VTEC power plant, delivering linear power delivery and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The close-ratio six-speed manual transmission exhibits zero grinds, with crisp gates and perfect synchro engagement. Mechanically impeccable, the chassis maintains its factory rigidity via the high-X-bone frame, supported by a fully refreshed double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal torque biasing. All VIN tags are present, and the undercarriage is free of oxidation, reflecting its climate-controlled storage history. The valvetrain is whisper-quiet with recent valve clearance adjustment, and the cooling system has been overhauled with OEM components. This is a rare, turn-key specimen for the discerning purist.",
